contentrichtext.text: {{Infobox Belgium Municipality |name=Onhaye |picture=Onhaye JPG00.jpg |picture-legend= |map=Onhaye Namur Belgium Map.png |map-legend=Location of Onhaye in Namur province |arms= |flag= |region={{BE-REG-WAL}} |community={{BE-FR}} |province={{BE-PROV-NM}} |arrondissement=[[Arrondissement of Dinant|Dinant]] |nis=91103 |pyramid-date= |0-19= |20-64= |65= |foreigners= |foreigners-date= |mayor=Christophe Bastin |majority= |postal-codes=5520-5524 |telephone-area=082 |web=[http://www.onhaye.be/ www.onhaye.be] |lat_deg=50 |lat_min=15 |lon_deg=04 |lon_min=50 }} '''Onhaye''' is a [[Wallonia|Walloon]] [[municipality]] located in the [[Belgium|Belgian]] province of [[Namur (province)|Namur]]. On January 1, 2006 Onhaye had a total population of 3,120. The total area is 65.53 km² which gives a [[population density]] of 48 inhabitants per km². [[File:0 Anthée - Château de Fontaine (1).JPG|thumb|left|[[Château de Fontaine]], west of Onhaye]] The region is home to several cultural heritage monuments, such as the fortified farmhouse [[Falaën Castle]]. {{Commons category|Onhaye}} ==References== {{reflist}} {{Namur}} [[Category:Municipalities of Namur (province)]] {{Namur-geo-stub}}
